00:42:59.440 --> 00:43:02.570 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't say that I'm
perfect at it, though.

00:43:02.570 --> 00:43:03.324 align:middle line:90%
How about you?

00:43:03.324 --> 00:43:04.290 align:middle line:90%
The main thing I've learned?

00:43:04.290 --> 00:43:05.137 align:middle line:90%
Mmhm.

00:43:05.137 --> 00:43:06.270 align:middle line:84%
You're gonna laugh
