00:43:15.920 --> 00:43:17.745 align:middle line:90%
but I didn't believe it myself.

00:43:17.745 --> 00:43:20.140 align:middle line:84%
It actually happened
after we broke up.

00:43:20.140 --> 00:43:22.190 align:middle line:90%
I decided you didn't deserve me.

00:43:22.190 --> 00:43:23.720 align:middle line:90%
I didn't deserve you?

00:43:23.720 --> 00:43:26.220 align:middle line:84%
Obviously, it was just
a defense mechanism.

00:43:26.220 --> 00:43:27.980 align:middle line:84%
It's what I told myself
to justify lot of things.

00:43:27.980 --> 00:43:30.050 align:middle line:84%
But now I know that
it doesn't have

00:43:30.050 --> 00:43:32.500 align:middle line:84%
to do with deserving
anyone or anything.

00:43:32.500 --> 00:43:36.000 align:middle line:84%
I brought you into my life, just
