00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:39.010 align:middle line:84%
And ultimately, it was
to learn about ourselves.

00:43:39.010 --> 00:43:41.000 align:middle line:84%
I want to stay with this
I didn't deserve you thing.

00:43:41.000 --> 00:43:42.220 align:middle line:90%
You really believe that?

00:43:42.220 --> 00:43:48.020 align:middle line:84%
Well, do you remember the last
