00:43:49.350 --> 00:43:50.350 align:middle line:90%
When I decided?

00:43:50.350 --> 00:43:52.181 align:middle line:90%
Of course.

00:43:52.181 --> 00:43:53.580 align:middle line:84%
You know I was just
sitting around waiting

00:43:53.580 --> 00:43:55.350 align:middle line:90%
