00:43:55.350 --> 00:43:57.410 align:middle line:84%
I know it sounds
said, but it's true.

00:43:57.410 --> 00:43:59.740 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, you said that we
weren't going to actually

00:43:59.740 --> 00:44:00.810 align:middle line:90%
be in a relationship.

00:44:00.810 --> 00:44:02.270 align:middle line:90%
We were going to be just lovers.

00:44:02.270 --> 00:44:04.284 align:middle line:84%
If I recall, that
