00:44:04.284 --> 00:44:05.750 align:middle line:84%
Well, that was just a
ploy to get you back.

00:44:05.750 --> 00:44:07.680 align:middle line:84%
KATHERINE: At least
you can admit it.

00:44:07.680 --> 00:44:10.430 align:middle line:84%
Well, I also told you
that I hoped that we'd

00:44:10.430 --> 00:44:12.450 align:middle line:84%
be able to say that we were
actually in a relationship

00:44:12.450 --> 00:44:13.770 align:middle line:90%
at some point.

00:44:13.770 --> 00:44:15.250 align:middle line:90%
I was very clear about that.

00:44:15.250 --> 00:44:16.930 align:middle line:84%
And every time, it started
to get intense-- good

00:44:16.930 --> 00:44:19.210 align:middle line:84%
