you had to remind me,

00:44:19.210 --> 00:44:23.000 align:middle line:84%
don't forget, we're not
actually in a relationship.

00:44:23.000 --> 00:44:24.170 align:middle line:84%
If I had more
respect for myself,

00:44:24.170 --> 00:44:26.290 align:middle line:84%
I would have said,
the hell with it.

00:44:26.290 --> 00:44:27.175 align:middle line:90%
I deserved more than that.

00:44:27.175 --> 00:44:30.320 align:middle line:84%
I deserve somebody who could
actually say the words.

00:44:30.320 --> 00:44:32.740 align:middle line:90%
Now you're pissing me off.

00:44:32.740 --> 00:44:35.030 align:middle line:84%
Like I said before,
that was your idea.

00:44:35.030 --> 00:44:37.170 align:middle line:90%
And I was honest with you too.

00:44:37.170 --> 00:44:39.490 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to jump back into
the way things were before.

00:44:39.490 --> 00:44:41.100 align:middle line:90%
I wanted to take it slower.

00:44:41.100 --> 00:44:43.310 align:middle line:84%
And there we were, right
back where we were before,

00:44:43.310 --> 00:44:45.225 align:middle line:84%
and I didn't think it was
worth taking the chance.

00:44:45.225 --> 00:44:47.810 align:middle line:90%
You never gave it a chance.

00:44:47.810 --> 00:44:49.530 align:middle line:84%
How in the hell was I
supposed to prove anything

00:44:49.530 --> 00:44:50.740 align:middle line:84%
when you had already
decided that everything

00:44:50.740 --> 00:44:51.550 align:middle line:90%
