00:44:51.550 --> 00:44:53.430 align:middle line:84%
KATHERINE: I hadn't
decided that.

00:44:53.430 --> 00:44:55.170 align:middle line:90%
I was open to you.

00:44:55.170 --> 00:44:58.090 align:middle line:84%
I was open to even being more
serious than we were before.

00:44:58.090 --> 00:45:00.000 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: What does that mean?

00:45:00.000 --> 00:45:03.800 align:middle line:84%
I was even open to
the idea of marriage.

00:45:03.800 --> 00:45:06.430 align:middle line:90%
The idea of marriage.

00:45:06.430 --> 00:45:08.200 align:middle line:84%
Marriage is more than
an idea, Catherine.

00:45:08.200 --> 00:45:11.340 align:middle line:84%
I was open to more
than the idea of it.

00:45:11.340 --> 00:45:13.140 align:middle line:84%
But I wasn't all hung up on
marriage like you thought.

00:45:13.140 --> 00:45:14.770 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't about that.

00:45:14.770 --> 00:45:16.864 align:middle line:84%
I would have liked to have been
able to have proven myself.

00:45:16.864 --> 00:45:17.730 align:middle line:90%
That would have been nice.

00:45:17.730 --> 00:45:19.470 align:middle line:84%
Why are you bringing
this all up now?

00:45:19.470 --> 00:45:20.893 align:middle line:90%
Why are you even here now?

00:45:20.893 --> 00:45:23.797 align:middle line:84%
I feel like my heart's
being torn open again.

00:45:23.797 --> 00:45:25.370 align:middle line:90%
Look, did You.

00:45:25.370 --> 00:45:27.950 align:middle line:84%
Think we were just going to
hang out for the afternoon

00:45:27.950 --> 00:45:31.670 align:middle line:84%
and just go home like nothing
ever happened between us?

00:45:31.670 --> 00:45:32.840 align:middle line:84%
Six years have
passed, and I feel

00:45:32.840 --> 00:45:34.415 align:middle line:90%
like you left me a month ago.

00:45:34.415 --> 00:45:36.440 align:middle line:84%
I thought it would be good
if we saw each other again.

00:45:36.440 --> 00:45:38.880 align:middle line:90%
It is good to see you again.

00:45:38.880 --> 00:45:40.760 align:middle line:90%
It's great to see you again.

00:45:40.760 --> 00:45:43.310 align:middle line:90%
And that's the problem.

00:45:43.310 --> 00:45:45.390 align:middle line:90%
Don't you remember why you left?

00:45:45.390 --> 00:45:46.830 align:middle line:84%
It's because we can't
seem to be together

00:45:46.830 --> 00:45:49.867 align:middle line:84%
without this amazing soul
thing happening between us.

00:45:49.867 --> 00:45:52.000 align:middle line:84%
You're like the one in the movie
that I loved before I was born.

00:45:52.000 --> 00:45:55.700 align:middle line:90%


00:45:55.700 --> 00:45:57.630 align:middle line:84%
Seeing you again just
reminds me of all that

00:45:57.630 --> 00:45:58.725 align:middle line:90%
and how nothing has changed.

00:45:58.725 --> 00:46:01.720 align:middle line:90%


00:46:01.720 --> 00:46:04.100 align:middle line:90%
Let's just stop for a minute.

00:46:04.100 --> 00:46:05.160 align:middle line:90%
I didn't want it to get this.

00:46:05.160 --> 00:46:07.150 align:middle line:84%
I thought it was important
that we'd see each other again.

00:46:07.150 --> 00:46:08.560 align:middle line:84%
And what am I supposed
to do with it now?

00:46:08.560 --> 00:46:10.570 align:middle line:84%
You-- you said before that
we didn't have to do anything

00:46:10.570 --> 00:46:12.290 align:middle line:90%
with it, except maybe honor it.

00:46:12.290 --> 00:46:13.970 align:middle line:84%
You just said that the
one thing you learned

00:46:13.970 --> 00:46:17.391 align:middle line:84%
was that you were a
great guy, and you are.

00:46:17.391 --> 00:46:19.290 align:middle line:84%
You said you realized that
you deserved a woman who would

00:46:19.290 --> 00:46:21.290 align:middle line:90%
feel blessed to be with you.

00:46:21.290 --> 00:46:24.080 align:middle line:84%
Obviously, you found
someone who feels that way.

00:46:24.080 --> 00:46:25.930 align:middle line:84%
You can be intimate
with her because you

00:46:25.930 --> 00:46:27.629 align:middle line:84%
