-Listen.

00:46:27.629 --> 00:46:29.300 align:middle line:84%
I'm sorry if I'm blowing
our little reunion,

00:46:29.300 --> 00:46:30.620 align:middle line:84%
but this is a lot
more difficult than I

00:46:30.620 --> 00:46:33.454 align:middle line:90%
thought I was going to be.

00:46:33.454 --> 00:46:35.020 align:middle line:84%
These things have been
kept inside for so long,

00:46:35.020 --> 00:46:36.660 align:middle line:84%
and now they're just
exploding out of me.

00:46:36.660 --> 00:46:38.901 align:middle line:84%
I-- I just want you to
know how much it fucking

00:46:38.901 --> 00:46:39.800 align:middle line:90%
hurt when you kept leaving.

00:46:39.800 --> 00:46:50.980 align:middle line:90%


00:46:50.980 --> 00:46:52.740 align:middle line:90%
I'm sorry.

00:46:52.740 --> 00:46:56.020 align:middle line:84%
But you know, this
is all good stuff.

00:46:56.020 --> 00:46:57.270 align:middle line:84%
