Of course.

00:47:15.580 --> 00:47:17.092 align:middle line:90%
Did you think I'd forget?

00:47:17.092 --> 00:47:18.895 align:middle line:90%
It all started here.

00:47:18.895 --> 00:47:21.420 align:middle line:90%
And ended here.

00:47:21.420 --> 00:47:23.170 align:middle line:84%
I didn't want to
come back here.

00:47:23.170 --> 00:47:24.335 align:middle line:90%
Too much for you?

00:47:24.335 --> 00:47:26.760 align:middle line:90%
