00:47:40.920 --> 00:47:43.640 align:middle line:90%
The first time we got together.

00:47:43.640 --> 00:47:44.340 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:47:44.340 --> 00:47:47.400 align:middle line:84%
I said that I wasn't
looking for a woman

00:47:47.400 --> 00:47:51.590 align:middle line:84%
to complete some
empty space inside me.

00:47:51.590 --> 00:47:54.650 align:middle line:84%
Looking back, I was
completely deluded.

00:47:54.650 --> 00:47:56.900 align:middle line:90%
Why do you say that?

00:47:56.900 --> 00:47:58.841 align:middle line:84%
You think we'd be doing
all this if that were true?

00:47:58.841 --> 00:48:02.810 align:middle line:84%
I don't know.
