it up, have you?

00:48:29.860 --> 00:48:31.110 align:middle line:90%
Of course not.

00:48:31.110 --> 00:48:31.825 align:middle line:90%
It's like a monument.

00:48:31.825 --> 00:48:35.690 align:middle line:90%


00:48:35.690 --> 00:48:38.540 align:middle line:84%
I remember the day you called
me and told me that you had

00:48:38.540 --> 00:48:41.270 align:middle line:84%
