You can't do something
to the symbol

00:49:29.870 --> 00:49:32.124 align:middle line:84%
and not expect it to
roll on into the reality.

00:49:32.124 --> 00:49:33.190 align:middle line:90%
KATHERINE: Your idea was better.

00:49:33.190 --> 00:49:34.860 align:middle line:90%
I know.

00:49:34.860 --> 00:49:36.190 align:middle line:84%
At least my idea was
a way of honoring

00:49:36.190 --> 00:49:37.056 align:middle line:90%
who we were to each other.

00:49:37.056 --> 00:49:39.990 align:middle line:90%


00:49:39.990 --> 00:49:43.260 align:middle line:84%
I swear, I can
feel it vibrating.

00:49:43.260 --> 00:49:44.686 align:middle line:90%
Give me your hand.

00:49:44.686 --> 00:49:51.530 align:middle line:90%


00:49:51.530 --> 00:49:54.460 align:middle line:90%
You really feel something?

00:49:54.460 --> 00:49:57.710 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, I think
about it, and it

00:49:57.710 --> 00:49:59.170 align:middle line:84%
makes me happy to
know that there's

00:49:59.170 --> 00:50:01.180 align:middle line:84%
this monument to how
much we love each other

00:50:01.180 --> 00:50:04.270 align:middle line:90%
that no one else knows about.

00:50:04.270 --> 00:50:05.770 align:middle line:84%
I mean, if I ever
wanted to, I could

00:50:05.770 --> 00:50:07.252 align:middle line:90%
just come back to this bench.

00:50:07.252 --> 00:50:10.210 align:middle line:90%


00:50:10.210 --> 00:50:11.714 align:middle line:90%
I've done that a lot.

00:50:11.714 --> 00:50:13.980 align:middle line:90%
KATHERINE: You have?

00:50:13.980 --> 00:50:15.310 align:middle line:84%
We come back to
Ashland every year,

00:50:15.310 --> 00:50:19.930 align:middle line:84%
and I always come back here
by myself and think about you

00:50:19.930 --> 00:50:22.710 align:middle line:84%
and think about
what you're doing.

00:50:22.710 --> 00:50:24.073 align:middle line:90%
And here we are now.

00:50:24.073 --> 00:50:26.440 align:middle line:90%
And here we are now.

00:50:26.440 --> 00:50:28.550 align:middle line:84%
Do you think we should
do something special?

00:50:28.550 --> 00:50:29.944 align:middle line:90%
Like what?

00:50:29.944 --> 00:50:31.010 align:middle line:90%
Maybe you could sing something?

00:50:31.010 --> 00:50:33.797 align:middle line:90%


00:50:33.797 --> 00:50:34.930 align:middle line:84%
I think just being
here's enough.

00:50:34.930 --> 00:50:37.910 align:middle line:90%


00:50:37.910 --> 00:50:40.468 align:middle line:84%
I feel like a new
chapter is beginning.

00:50:40.468 --> 00:50:43.360 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: How do you mean?

00:50:43.360 --> 00:50:46.120 align:middle line:84%
KATHERINE: The fact
that we're here

00:50:46.120 --> 00:50:48.345 align:middle line:90%
