00:50:48.345 --> 00:50:50.720 align:middle line:84%
And there's still this
energy between us,

00:50:50.720 --> 00:50:55.220 align:middle line:90%
and these hands are radiating.

00:50:55.220 --> 00:50:57.080 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

00:50:57.080 --> 00:50:59.175 align:middle line:84%
Just feels like something
new is beginning.

00:50:59.175 --> 00:51:01.270 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: I like that idea.

00:51:01.270 --> 00:51:02.680 align:middle line:90%
You do?

00:51:02.680 --> 00:51:05.411 align:middle line:90%
Does that surprise you?

00:51:05.411 --> 00:51:06.810 align:middle line:84%
I was always concerned
about hurting you.

00:51:06.810 --> 00:51:08.870 align:middle line:84%
I thought that this
might be too much.

00:51:08.870 --> 00:51:09.970 align:middle line:84%
FREDRICK: It is
in a lot of ways.

00:51:09.970 --> 00:51:13.337 align:middle line:90%


00:51:13.337 --> 00:51:14.780 align:middle line:90%
It's OK.

00:51:14.780 --> 00:51:16.704 align:middle line:90%
You said what you needed to.

00:51:16.704 --> 00:51:17.666 align:middle line:90%
I did.

00:51:17.666 --> 00:51:21.520 align:middle line:90%


00:51:21.520 --> 00:51:23.260 align:middle line:84%
Do you think we
could stay in touch

00:51:23.260 --> 00:51:25.760 align:middle line:90%
and have it still be healthy?

00:51:25.760 --> 00:51:26.630 align:middle line:90%
I don't know.

00:51:26.630 --> 00:51:29.014 align:middle line:90%
Part of me thinks it'd be fine.

00:51:29.014 --> 00:51:30.580 align:middle line:84%
Another part wonders if
I'll ever be able to be

00:51:30.580 --> 00:51:32.512 align:middle line:90%
just friends with you.

00:51:32.512 --> 00:51:35.360 align:middle line:90%
You're probably right.

00:51:35.360 --> 00:51:37.591 align:middle line:84%
So how's this book
of yours going to end?

00:51:37.591 --> 00:51:40.310 align:middle line:84%
I don't know.
I haven't decided yet.

00:51:40.310 --> 00:51:42.115 align:middle line:90%
Is all this gonna be in it?

00:51:42.115 --> 00:51:44.610 align:middle line:84%
At first, I didn't
think so, but now I do.

00:51:44.610 --> 00:51:46.410 align:middle line:90%
It's a perfect ending.

00:51:46.410 --> 00:51:48.386 align:middle line:90%
That's what we never had.

00:51:48.386 --> 00:51:51.284 align:middle line:90%
Do we ever really end?

00:51:51.284 --> 00:51:53.710 align:middle line:90%
I hope not.

00:51:53.710 --> 00:51:56.100 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: I doubt it.

00:51:56.100 --> 00:51:58.045 align:middle line:84%
You can't change someone's
life the way that we have

00:51:58.045 --> 00:51:59.995 align:middle line:84%
and just wrap it up in
some tidy little ending.

00:51:59.995 --> 00:52:02.910 align:middle line:90%


00:52:02.910 --> 00:52:05.410 align:middle line:84%
Well, I never thought you
and I would be legendary.

00:52:05.410 --> 00:52:06.345 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: Legendary fools.

00:52:06.345 --> 00:52:08.200 align:middle line:90%
Why do you say that?

00:52:08.200 --> 00:52:11.960 align:middle line:84%
Well, we've been fools
for love, especially me.

00:52:11.960 --> 00:52:15.120 align:middle line:84%
I carried you around
with me for six years.

00:52:15.120 --> 00:52:16.490 align:middle line:84%
It reminds me of
this story that I

00:52:16.490 --> 00:52:19.130 align:middle line:84%
heard about these
two Buddhist monks,

00:52:19.130 --> 00:52:21.570 align:middle line:90%
one very old, one very young.

00:52:21.570 --> 00:52:23.440 align:middle line:84%
And they're walking
along the river bank,

00:52:23.440 --> 00:52:25.850 align:middle line:84%
and they see this
beautiful woman.

00:52:25.850 --> 00:52:28.000 align:middle line:84%
And she needs to get
to the other side.

00:52:28.000 --> 00:52:30.845 align:middle line:84%
So the older monk decides
that they should carry

00:52:30.845 --> 00:52:33.610 align:middle line:90%
her across, which they do.

00:52:33.610 --> 00:52:35.680 align:middle line:84%
And they're walk along
for about an hour.

00:52:35.680 --> 00:52:38.567 align:middle line:84%
And the younger one hasn't
said anything in a long time.

00:52:38.567 --> 00:52:39.900 align:middle line:84%
And then finally, he
looks at his elder,

00:52:39.900 --> 00:52:41.790 align:middle line:84%
and he says, why
did you force us

00:52:41.790 --> 00:52:45.390 align:middle line:84%
to break our vows by carrying
that woman across the river?

00:52:45.390 --> 00:52:49.160 align:middle line:84%
And the older one looks at him
and he smiles, and he says,

00:52:49.160 --> 00:52:52.254 align:middle line:84%
I set that woman down when
I got to the other side.

00:52:52.254 --> 00:52:53.520 align:middle line:84%
Why are you still
carrying her around?

00:52:53.520 --> 00:53:00.060 align:middle line:90%


00:53:00.060 --> 00:53:01.572 align:middle line:90%
Time to set me down.

00:53:01.572 --> 00:53:02.516 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: Yeah.

00:53:02.516 --> 00:53:03.460 align:middle line:90%
It's time.

00:53:03.460 --> 00:53:09.124 align:middle line:90%


00:53:09.124 --> 00:53:11.090 align:middle line:90%
How long you in town?

00:53:11.090 --> 00:53:13.340 align:middle line:90%
I leave tonight.

00:53:13.340 --> 00:53:16.810 align:middle line:84%
I think I've finished
what I needed to complete.

00:53:16.810 --> 00:53:19.620 align:middle line:90%
How about you?

00:53:19.620 --> 00:53:22.510 align:middle line:84%
I'm gonna stick around for a
few days, visit a few friends,

00:53:22.510 --> 00:53:24.450 align:middle line:90%
maybe see a play.

00:53:24.450 --> 00:53:25.670 align:middle line:90%
I still love this town.

00:53:25.670 --> 00:53:27.735 align:middle line:84%
It's the best
place I ever lived.

00:53:27.735 --> 00:53:30.060 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes I wonder
why I ever left.

00:53:30.060 --> 00:53:32.860 align:middle line:90%


00:53:32.860 --> 00:53:34.361 align:middle line:90%
Wanna get going?

00:53:34.361 --> 00:53:35.560 align:middle line:84%
Do you think we
should do something

00:53:35.560 --> 00:53:37.556 align:middle line:90%
special with the hands?

00:53:37.556 --> 00:53:38.900 align:middle line:90%
I think we already have.

00:53:38.900 --> 00:53:41.270 align:middle line:90%
What did we do?

00:53:41.270 --> 00:53:43.652 align:middle line:84%
Well, I think maybe now
they can rest in peace.

00:53:43.652 --> 00:53:46.604 align:middle line:90%


00:53:46.604 --> 00:53:47.588 align:middle line:90%
Feel it again.

00:53:47.588 --> 00:53:55.460 align:middle line:90%


00:53:55.460 --> 00:53:57.630 align:middle line:90%
It feels calmer.

00:53:57.630 --> 00:54:00.116 align:middle line:90%
FREDRICK: Is that a good thing?

00:54:00.116 --> 00:54:01.064 align:middle line:90%
I think so.

00:54:01.064 --> 00:54:06.280 align:middle line:90%


00:54:06.280 --> 00:54:08.675 align:middle line:84%
So do I get to
look at this book

00:54:08.675 --> 00:54:10.280 align:middle line:84%
before everybody else
in the world reads it?

00:54:10.280 --> 00:54:11.410 align:middle line:90%
Nope.

00:54:11.410 --> 00:54:12.510 align:middle line:90%
Why not?

00:54:12.510 --> 00:54:14.180 align:middle line:84%
Because it's from
my perspective.

00:54:14.180 --> 00:54:15.770 align:middle line:84%
It doesn't have
anything to do with you.

00:54:15.770 --> 00:54:17.520 align:middle line:84%
How could it not have
anything to do with me?

00:54:17.520 --> 00:54:19.850 align:middle line:84%
Because everything
I write is about me.

00:54:19.850 --> 00:54:21.610 align:middle line:90%
That's what intimacy is.

00:54:21.610 --> 00:54:22.650 align:middle line:90%
Into-me-see.

00:54:22.650 --> 00:54:24.490 align:middle line:90%
You like that, eh?

00:54:24.490 --> 00:54:25.800 align:middle line:90%
It's cute.

00:54:25.800 --> 00:54:27.120 align:middle line:90%
But I don't know if it's fair.

00:54:27.120 --> 00:54:30.030 align:middle line:90%
Life is never fair.

00:54:30.030 --> 00:54:31.720 align:middle line:84%
Maybe I'll make
a movie about us.

00:54:31.720 --> 00:54:32.660 align:middle line:90%
A movie?

00:54:32.660 --> 00:54:34.780 align:middle line:90%
Would that surprise you?

00:54:34.780 --> 00:54:36.630 align:middle line:84%
No, nothing you did
would ever surprise me.

00:54:36.630 --> 00:54:37.920 align:middle line:90%
It never has.

00:54:37.920 --> 00:54:40.925 align:middle line:84%
This is a great story,
but the ending sucks.

00:54:40.925 --> 00:54:42.350 align:middle line:90%
The ending doesn't suck.

00:54:42.350 --> 00:54:44.640 align:middle line:84%
Years later, they meet,
reconcile the past,

00:54:44.640 --> 00:54:46.760 align:middle line:90%
and go their separate ways.

00:54:46.760 --> 00:54:47.560 align:middle line:90%
That sucks.

00:54:47.560 --> 00:54:50.810 align:middle line:84%
It would suck even more if
it had a Hollywood ending.

00:54:50.810 --> 00:54:53.100 align:middle line:84%
Credits roll as we ride
off into the sunset?

00:54:53.100 --> 00:54:54.640 align:middle line:90%
Unrealistic.

00:54:54.640 --> 00:54:56.373 align:middle line:84%
I was always the romantic
one in this relationship.

00:54:56.373 --> 00:54:58.670 align:middle line:84%
If that were true, your
movie would be a comedy.

00:54:58.670 --> 00:55:01.300 align:middle line:90%


00:55:01.300 --> 00:55:02.862 align:middle line:90%
So there you have it.

00:55:02.862 --> 00:55:04.870 align:middle line:84%
It's probably not the
ending a lot of you wanted,

00:55:04.870 --> 00:55:08.150 align:middle line:90%
but that's really how life is.

00:55:08.150 --> 00:55:10.330 align:middle line:84%
Perfect doesn't mean that
everybody gets back together

00:55:10.330 --> 00:55:12.430 align:middle line:90%
and lives happily ever after.

00:55:12.430 --> 00:55:14.490 align:middle line:84%
It's more about accepting
what really happens

00:55:14.490 --> 00:55:16.356 align:middle line:90%
and just getting on with living.

00:55:16.356 --> 00:55:18.560 align:middle line:84%
And by the way, the thing
I said before about getting

00:55:18.560 --> 00:55:21.290 align:middle line:84%
over this pretty quick--
in retrospect, that

00:55:21.290 --> 00:55:23.380 align:middle line:90%
probably wasn't very smart.

00:55:23.380 --> 00:55:24.815 align:middle line:84%
These things take as
long as they take,

00:55:24.815 --> 00:55:27.360 align:middle line:84%
and there's nothing we
can do to rush them.

00:55:27.360 --> 00:55:29.000 align:middle line:84%
But in the end,
we have the chance

00:55:29.000 --> 00:55:31.290 align:middle line:84%
to look back over our lives
and see some of the things we

00:55:31.290 --> 00:55:33.690 align:middle line:90%
missed the first time around.

00:55:33.690 --> 00:55:38.190 align:middle line:84%
Hopefully, we learn a lesson or
two and we get a little wiser.

00:55:38.190 --> 00:55:41.370 align:middle line:84%
As for those hands,
well, let's just

00:55:41.370 --> 00:55:44.190 align:middle line:84%
say that they're going to
be around as a reminder.

00:55:44.190 --> 00:55:46.230 align:middle line:84%
We just have to make
a choice about which

00:55:46.230 --> 00:55:50.480 align:middle line:84%
monk we want to be-- either
the one who set her down

00:55:50.480 --> 00:55:51.855 align:middle line:84%
or the one who's
still carrying her.

00:55:51.855 --> 00:55:54.090 align:middle line:84%
It's one of those choices
that we all have to make

00:55:54.090 --> 00:55:55.020 align:middle line:90%
at one point or another.

00:55:55.020 --> 00:56:18.828 align:middle line:90%


00:56:18.828 --> 00:56:21.804 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE AND CHEERING]

00:56:21.804 --> 00:56:23.788 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:23.788 --> 00:56:25.772 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:25.772 --> 00:56:27.260 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:27.260 --> 00:56:28.252 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:28.252 --> 00:56:29.290 align:middle line:90%
Thank you very much.

00:56:29.290 --> 00:56:30.890 align:middle line:84%
I'm the director,
and I appreciate

00:56:30.890 --> 00:56:33.190 align:middle line:84%
very much your being here
tonight for the premier

00:56:33.190 --> 00:56:34.700 align:middle line:90%
of "Into Me See."

00:56:34.700 --> 00:56:36.230 align:middle line:84%
It's been a wonderful
evening for all of us,

00:56:36.230 --> 00:56:37.830 align:middle line:84%
and we're going to
continue the good times now

00:56:37.830 --> 00:56:38.790 align:middle line:90%
next door in the restaurant.

00:56:38.790 --> 00:56:39.823 align:middle line:90%
There'll be a little reception.

00:56:39.823 --> 00:56:41.633 align:middle line:84%
We'll get some wine
and cheese out for you,

00:56:41.633 --> 00:56:43.566 align:middle line:84%
and then we'll answer some
questions and schmooze a little

00:56:43.566 --> 00:56:44.480 align:middle line:90%
and just have a good time.

00:56:44.480 --> 00:56:45.380 align:middle line:90%
So we'll see you there, OK?

00:56:45.380 --> 00:56:46.770 align:middle line:84%
And thanks again for
being here tonight.

00:56:46.770 --> 00:56:47.774 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

00:56:47.774 --> 00:56:50.244 align:middle line:90%
[APPLAUSE AND CHEERING]

00:56:50.244 --> 00:56:52.714 align:middle line:84%
Thanks, sweetheart.
Thank you.

00:56:52.714 --> 00:57:13.000 align:middle line:90%


00:57:13.000 --> 00:57:14.360 align:middle line:90%
Oh, you scared me.

00:57:14.360 --> 00:57:15.380 align:middle line:90%
I thought I was alone in here.

00:57:15.380 --> 00:57:16.930 align:middle line:90%
I thought everyone had left.

00:57:16.930 --> 00:57:17.760 align:middle line:90%
I'll live in a minute.

00:57:17.760 --> 00:57:20.521 align:middle line:84%
I just wanted to
say hello first.

00:57:20.521 --> 00:57:24.940 align:middle line:90%


00:57:24.940 --> 00:57:25.797 align:middle line:90%
My god.

00:57:25.797 --> 00:57:29.533 align:middle line:90%


00:57:29.533 --> 00:57:32.340 align:middle line:90%
Oh my god.

00:57:32.340 --> 00:57:35.290 align:middle line:84%
I didn't think
you'd recognize me.

00:57:35.290 --> 00:57:38.470 align:middle line:90%
Are you kidding?

00:57:38.470 --> 00:57:39.970 align:middle line:90%
Come over here.

00:57:39.970 --> 00:57:53.658 align:middle line:90%


00:57:53.658 --> 00:57:54.800 align:middle line:90%
BOTH: You look great.

00:57:54.800 --> 00:57:57.461 align:middle line:90%


00:57:57.461 --> 00:57:58.980 align:middle line:84%
No, but you do.
You really do.

00:57:58.980 --> 00:57:59.930 align:middle line:90%
So do you.

00:57:59.930 --> 00:58:02.780 align:middle line:90%


00:58:02.780 --> 00:58:04.190 align:middle line:90%
How long has it been?

00:58:04.190 --> 00:58:05.590 align:middle line:84%
20 years?
-22.

00:58:05.590 --> 00:58:06.430 align:middle line:90%
But who's counting?

00:58:06.430 --> 00:58:09.100 align:middle line:90%


00:58:09.100 --> 00:58:10.900 align:middle line:84%
So how'd you find
out about this?

00:58:10.900 --> 00:58:12.850 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you think I'm going
to reveal my secret?

00:58:12.850 --> 00:58:13.580 align:middle line:90%
I don't think so.

00:58:13.580 --> 00:58:15.820 align:middle line:84%
I think I'm going to let
you suffer a little more.

00:58:15.820 --> 00:58:17.905 align:middle line:84%
Oh, so we're back to letting
me suffer again, are we?

00:58:17.905 --> 00:58:20.632 align:middle line:84%
You know what I really
want to know is why you

00:58:20.632 --> 00:58:22.540 align:middle line:90%
did this after so many years.

00:58:22.540 --> 00:58:24.840 align:middle line:84%
I would have thought
you would have moved on.

00:58:24.840 --> 00:58:27.096 align:middle line:90%
I did move on, completely.

00:58:27.096 --> 00:58:31.390 align:middle line:84%
I just wanted to revisit the
moment, I guess, one more time.

00:58:31.390 --> 00:58:33.090 align:middle line:84%
Or maybe I got tired
of waiting for the book

00:58:33.090 --> 00:58:34.930 align:middle line:90%
that you never wrote.

00:58:34.930 --> 00:58:36.361 align:middle line:84%
I tried to write it.
I did.

00:58:36.361 --> 00:58:37.060 align:middle line:90%
I did.

00:58:37.060 --> 00:58:39.190 align:middle line:84%
But I just was never
happy with what came out.

00:58:39.190 --> 00:58:41.000 align:middle line:84%
Yeah, well, somebody
had to tell our story.

00:58:41.000 --> 00:58:42.270 align:middle line:90%
So I thought I'd be the one.

00:58:42.270 --> 00:58:43.302 align:middle line:90%
Why?

00:58:43.302 --> 00:58:45.560 align:middle line:90%
Why was it so important?

00:58:45.560 --> 00:58:51.210 align:middle line:84%
Why was it-- you really
don't know, do you?

00:58:51.210 --> 00:58:52.400 align:middle line:84%
Ours was one of
the most important

00:58:52.400 --> 00:58:53.844 align:middle line:90%
relationships in my life.

00:58:53.844 --> 00:58:55.310 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't know anything
about relationships

00:58:55.310 --> 00:58:57.130 align:middle line:90%
if it hadn't been for you.

00:58:57.130 --> 00:59:00.340 align:middle line:90%
You mean that.

00:59:00.340 --> 00:59:01.970 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

00:59:01.970 --> 00:59:02.756 align:middle line:90%
I mean it.

00:59:02.756 --> 00:59:06.570 align:middle line:90%


00:59:06.570 --> 00:59:08.320 align:middle line:84%
They pause awkwardly,
look at each other,

00:59:08.320 --> 00:59:12.500 align:middle line:84%
and she goes on, changing
the subject abruptly.

00:59:12.500 --> 00:59:13.820 align:middle line:90%
So, um--

00:59:13.820 --> 00:59:16.760 align:middle line:90%


00:59:16.760 --> 00:59:17.480 align:middle line:90%
Nothing to say.

00:59:17.480 --> 00:59:18.660 align:middle line:90%
No.

00:59:18.660 --> 00:59:22.360 align:middle line:84%
Well, let's get out of here.
CATHERINE: Let's see.

00:59:22.360 --> 00:59:23.910 align:middle line:90%
Where are you today?

00:59:23.910 --> 00:59:25.870 align:middle line:90%
You've been married 23 years.

00:59:25.870 --> 00:59:27.860 align:middle line:84%
Came back to Ashland
10 years ago,

00:59:27.860 --> 00:59:30.260 align:middle line:84%
started your art magazine
five years ago, which is

00:59:30.260 --> 00:59:32.650 align:middle line:90%
now read by half the country.

00:59:32.650 --> 00:59:33.900 align:middle line:90%
Your daughter's 20.

00:59:33.900 --> 00:59:36.310 align:middle line:84%
And if I'm not mistaken, you're
gonna be a grandfather soon.

00:59:36.310 --> 00:59:37.630 align:middle line:90%
I am very impressed.

00:59:37.630 --> 00:59:38.820 align:middle line:90%
You're impressed?

00:59:38.820 --> 00:59:40.150 align:middle line:90%
I'm impressed.

00:59:40.150 --> 00:59:41.644 align:middle line:90%
How do you know all that stuff?

00:59:41.644 --> 00:59:42.810 align:middle line:84%
You drop off the
face of the Earth,

00:59:42.810 --> 00:59:44.474 align:middle line:90%
you know everything about me.

00:59:44.474 --> 00:59:45.270 align:middle line:90%
Hm.

00:59:45.270 --> 00:59:47.003 align:middle line:84%
You're not going to tell
me that all the while I've

00:59:47.003 --> 00:59:50.690 align:middle line:84%
been following your life, you've
been following mine, are you?

00:59:50.690 --> 00:59:52.630 align:middle line:90%
Jesus.

00:59:52.630 --> 00:59:53.600 align:middle line:90%
All right.

00:59:53.600 --> 00:59:54.530 align:middle line:90%
I'll ask you a second time.

00:59:54.530 --> 00:59:56.470 align:middle line:90%
How did you find out about this?

00:59:56.470 --> 00:59:58.130 align:middle line:84%
Well, just because
you're not creative enough

00:59:58.130 --> 01:00:00.030 align:middle line:84%
to track someone down
doesn't mean I'm not.

01:00:00.030 --> 01:00:01.610 align:middle line:84%
I guess it depends
on how much one

01:00:01.610 --> 01:00:03.390 align:middle line:90%
wants to, how much one cares.

01:00:03.390 --> 01:00:05.190 align:middle line:84%
It's not about caring.
It's about courage.

01:00:05.190 --> 01:00:08.030 align:middle line:90%


01:00:08.030 --> 01:00:10.420 align:middle line:84%
Well, I-- I guess
the name change might

01:00:10.420 --> 01:00:12.480 align:middle line:84%
have tripped you up a little.
-No kidding.

01:00:12.480 --> 01:00:14.260 align:middle line:84%
Why didn't you tell me.
Is he here?

01:00:14.260 --> 01:00:15.500 align:middle line:84%
Oh, yeah.
He's here.

01:00:15.500 --> 01:00:16.380 align:middle line:90%
He saw the whole film.

01:00:16.380 --> 01:00:17.260 align:middle line:90%
He saw it?

01:00:17.260 --> 01:00:18.460 align:middle line:90%
What did he think of it?

01:00:18.460 --> 01:00:22.620 align:middle line:90%
Well, he loved me, hated you.

01:00:22.620 --> 01:00:24.290 align:middle line:84%
Well, how long have
you guys been in town?

01:00:24.290 --> 01:00:25.580 align:middle line:90%
Oh, a couple of days.

01:00:25.580 --> 01:00:27.085 align:middle line:84%
We've just been
wandering around.

01:00:27.085 --> 01:00:28.020 align:middle line:90%
A couple of days?

01:00:28.020 --> 01:00:29.170 align:middle line:90%
Uh-huh.

01:00:29.170 --> 01:00:31.062 align:middle line:84%
I even saw you in
the park yesterday.

01:00:31.062 --> 01:00:32.540 align:middle line:90%
You saw me?

01:00:32.540 --> 01:00:33.855 align:middle line:90%
Well, why didn't you stop me?

01:00:33.855 --> 01:00:35.230 align:middle line:84%
We could have had
lunch or something.

01:00:35.230 --> 01:00:36.180 align:middle line:84%
I know.
I know.

01:00:36.180 --> 01:00:38.600 align:middle line:84%
It was hard.
It was so hard.

01:00:38.600 --> 01:00:41.010 align:middle line:84%
But I really wanted
to surprise you here.

01:00:41.010 --> 01:00:41.820 align:middle line:90%
You did that.

01:00:41.820 --> 01:00:43.726 align:middle line:90%
You blew me away.

01:00:43.726 --> 01:00:45.010 align:middle line:90%
Wait a minute.

01:00:45.010 --> 01:00:47.090 align:middle line:90%
You saw me in the park?

01:00:47.090 --> 01:00:49.147 align:middle line:84%
While I was sitting
on that bench?

01:00:49.147 --> 01:00:49.901 align:middle line:90%
Uh-huh.

01:00:49.901 --> 01:00:53.360 align:middle line:84%
That exact same bench.
-Yeah.

01:00:53.360 --> 01:00:56.100 align:middle line:90%


01:00:56.100 --> 01:00:57.870 align:middle line:90%
You caught me.

01:00:57.870 --> 01:00:59.870 align:middle line:84%
I mean, I sit on that
bench all the time.

01:00:59.870 --> 01:01:02.170 align:middle line:90%
I have.

01:01:02.170 --> 01:01:05.050 align:middle line:90%
For a lot of years.

01:01:05.050 --> 01:01:06.940 align:middle line:84%
Every time I sit
on that bench, it's

01:01:06.940 --> 01:01:09.362 align:middle line:84%
like when we were
there together, you

01:01:09.362 --> 01:01:11.580 align:middle line:90%
and me, on that day.

01:01:11.580 --> 01:01:12.900 align:middle line:90%
That day.

01:01:12.900 --> 01:01:14.996 align:middle line:90%
That day you put on film.

01:01:14.996 --> 01:01:18.460 align:middle line:84%
It was so strange, watching
it and seeing every moment

01:01:18.460 --> 01:01:20.320 align:middle line:84%
just as I remembered
them all these years.

01:01:20.320 --> 01:01:21.670 align:middle line:84%
Well, it's nice
to know you didn't

01:01:21.670 --> 01:01:23.140 align:middle line:90%
let those memories fade away.

01:01:23.140 --> 01:01:24.444 align:middle line:84%
Oh, did you really
think I would?

01:01:24.444 --> 01:01:25.710 align:middle line:84%
Did you really think
I would just walk

01:01:25.710 --> 01:01:27.050 align:middle line:90%
away and forget all about you?

01:01:27.050 --> 01:01:27.765 align:middle line:90%
JAMES: Yes, I did.

01:01:27.765 --> 01:01:28.750 align:middle line:90%
I-- I sometimes thought that.

01:01:28.750 --> 01:01:29.883 align:middle line:84%
What else was I
supposed to think?

01:01:29.883 --> 01:01:31.165 align:middle line:90%
Well, you were wrong.

01:01:31.165 --> 01:01:32.890 align:middle line:84%
And one of the things
I wanted to tell you--

01:01:32.890 --> 01:01:34.800 align:middle line:84%
the most important thing
I wanted to tell you

01:01:34.800 --> 01:01:38.070 align:middle line:84%
was all that time I was
throwing that word around,

01:01:38.070 --> 01:01:42.810 align:middle line:84%
intimacy, and feeling
like it was about finding

01:01:42.810 --> 01:01:44.400 align:middle line:90%
myself and me finding me.

01:01:44.400 --> 01:01:46.000 align:middle line:84%
And that is true, and
that is important.

01:01:46.000 --> 01:01:53.700 align:middle line:84%
But what that word also means
is having someone else see me.

01:01:53.700 --> 01:01:56.550 align:middle line:90%
Letting someone else see you.

01:01:56.550 --> 01:01:58.733 align:middle line:90%
Letting someone else see me.

01:01:58.733 --> 01:02:03.830 align:middle line:90%


01:02:03.830 --> 01:02:04.529 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:02:04.529 --> 01:02:08.393 align:middle line:90%


01:02:08.393 --> 01:02:09.765 align:middle line:84%
It feels good to
hear you say that.

01:02:09.765 --> 01:02:13.690 align:middle line:84%
It really feels good
to be able to say that.

01:02:13.690 --> 01:02:15.210 align:middle line:84%
JAMES: So now, you know
why I made this film.

01:02:15.210 --> 01:02:16.266 align:middle line:90%
Now, you understood.

01:02:16.266 --> 01:02:17.100 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

01:02:17.100 --> 01:02:18.360 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know how
I'd feel about it.

01:02:18.360 --> 01:02:21.630 align:middle line:84%
But oh, I was so touched
that you would remember.

01:02:21.630 --> 01:02:24.520 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you didn't forget, but
you thought that I would?

01:02:24.520 --> 01:02:27.450 align:middle line:84%
Well, I thought you
might want to, more.

01:02:27.450 --> 01:02:32.072 align:middle line:90%
Well, I did, for a long time.

01:02:32.072 --> 01:02:34.800 align:middle line:90%
But you know, years go by.

01:02:34.800 --> 01:02:36.470 align:middle line:84%
I got into my soul
space about it.

01:02:36.470 --> 01:02:37.959 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHS]
No, really.

01:02:37.959 --> 01:02:40.190 align:middle line:84%
I thought it was
probably perfect that it

01:02:40.190 --> 01:02:41.760 align:middle line:90%
worked out that way in the end.

01:02:41.760 --> 01:02:42.830 align:middle line:90%
Part of our evolution.

01:02:42.830 --> 01:02:43.810 align:middle line:90%
Yeah.

01:02:43.810 --> 01:02:45.410 align:middle line:90%
I know.

01:02:45.410 --> 01:02:46.490 align:middle line:90%
I mean, it is hard at first.

01:02:46.490 --> 01:02:48.410 align:middle line:84%
We always think our hearts
are never going to mend.

01:02:48.410 --> 01:02:49.890 align:middle line:90%
But they do.

01:02:49.890 --> 01:02:51.620 align:middle line:90%
New people come into our lives.

01:02:51.620 --> 01:02:52.630 align:middle line:90%
Things change.

01:02:52.630 --> 01:02:59.620 align:middle line:84%
We-- but you never do
forget those who have meant

01:02:59.620 --> 01:03:01.203 align:middle line:90%
so much to you before, do you?

01:03:01.203 --> 01:03:04.941 align:middle line:90%


01:03:04.941 --> 01:03:05.640 align:middle line:90%
No.

01:03:05.640 --> 01:03:10.090 align:middle line:90%


01:03:10.090 --> 01:03:13.080 align:middle line:90%
Well, I'm glad I came.

01:03:13.080 --> 01:03:16.990 align:middle line:90%


01:03:16.990 --> 01:03:20.680 align:middle line:90%
So am I.

01:03:20.680 --> 01:03:23.540 align:middle line:84%
Oh, and I, um-- I did something
that you might not agree with.

01:03:23.540 --> 01:03:25.010 align:middle line:84%
JAMES: What did
you do, Catherine?

01:03:25.010 --> 01:03:28.380 align:middle line:84%
Well, I thought it was time
for a little archaeological dig.

01:03:28.380 --> 01:03:30.635 align:middle line:84%
You're not gonna tell you went
back to that park after I left,

01:03:30.635 --> 01:03:31.334 align:middle line:90%
are you?

01:03:31.334 --> 01:03:34.180 align:middle line:84%
I knew you'd made this film,
which was your way of blessing

01:03:34.180 --> 01:03:35.170 align:middle line:90%
what happened between us.

01:03:35.170 --> 01:03:37.630 align:middle line:84%
And I just had to
find my own way.

01:03:37.630 --> 01:03:40.921 align:middle line:84%
I thought it was time we let
those hands breathe again.

01:03:40.921 --> 01:03:41.620 align:middle line:90%
Catherine.

01:03:41.620 --> 01:03:46.134 align:middle line:84%
Of course, it's been 28 years,
and nature being what it is--

01:03:46.134 --> 01:03:47.786 align:middle line:90%
JAMES: What the hell is this?

01:03:47.786 --> 01:03:49.600 align:middle line:90%
CATHERINE: It's all that's left.

01:03:49.600 --> 01:03:52.700 align:middle line:84%
There was a lot of white
dust mixed with the dirt.

01:03:52.700 --> 01:03:56.350 align:middle line:84%
I guess time has its way with
everything, including us.

01:03:56.350 --> 01:04:01.670 align:middle line:84%
Anyway, something for
you to remember me by.

01:04:01.670 --> 01:04:04.320 align:middle line:84%
Catherine, I can't believe
after all these years,

01:04:04.320 --> 01:04:05.640 align:middle line:84%
you've finally
given me the finger.

01:04:05.640 --> 01:04:12.360 align:middle line:90%


01:04:12.360 --> 01:04:16.896 align:middle line:84%
I don't know whether this is
right or completely wrong.

01:04:16.896 --> 01:04:18.340 align:middle line:84%
No, it's right.
It's right.

01:04:18.340 --> 01:04:20.580 align:middle line:90%
At least, I think it is.

01:04:20.580 --> 01:04:23.740 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we'd buried those
hands all those years ago.

01:04:23.740 --> 01:04:25.800 align:middle line:90%
But it's not about the hands.

01:04:25.800 --> 01:04:28.280 align:middle line:84%
It's about the lessons we've
learned from each other,

01:04:28.280 --> 01:04:33.260 align:middle line:84%
and those are just--
those are priceless.

01:04:33.260 --> 01:04:37.190 align:middle line:84%
And it's just nice,
when you think about it.

01:04:37.190 --> 01:04:39.445 align:middle line:84%
SUSAN: Sweetheart,
everyone's waiting for you.

01:04:39.445 --> 01:04:40.145 align:middle line:90%
What's taking you--

01:04:40.145 --> 01:04:41.911 align:middle line:84%
Darling, this is someone
I want to introduce you to.

01:04:41.911 --> 01:04:43.781 align:middle line:84%
Oh, you don't need to
tell me who this is.

01:04:43.781 --> 01:04:45.791 align:middle line:84%
Catherine.
-Hi.

01:04:45.791 --> 01:04:46.490 align:middle line:90%
Whoa, wait a minute.

01:04:46.490 --> 01:04:47.456 align:middle line:90%
You two guys know each other?

01:04:47.456 --> 01:04:49.000 align:middle line:90%
When did you get to town?

01:04:49.000 --> 01:04:50.140 align:middle line:90%
Oh, we just came in early.

01:04:50.140 --> 01:04:51.430 align:middle line:90%
I've been here a couple of days.

01:04:51.430 --> 01:04:52.530 align:middle line:90%
Of course.

01:04:52.530 --> 01:04:53.890 align:middle line:90%
This is how you found out.

01:04:53.890 --> 01:04:55.190 align:middle line:90%
That's right, James.

01:04:55.190 --> 01:04:56.850 align:middle line:90%
I did what you didn't do.

01:04:56.850 --> 01:04:57.920 align:middle line:90%
I found her.

01:04:57.920 --> 01:04:58.770 align:middle line:90%
Hey, no fair.

01:04:58.770 --> 01:04:59.870 align:middle line:84%
She got married.
She changed her name.

01:04:59.870 --> 01:05:00.569 align:middle line:90%
How'd you find her?

01:05:00.569 --> 01:05:03.590 align:middle line:84%
A woman things past the
end of her nose, darling.

01:05:03.590 --> 01:05:05.420 align:middle line:84%
Courthouse has the
record of every marriage

01:05:05.420 --> 01:05:07.530 align:middle line:90%
for the last 100 years.

01:05:07.530 --> 01:05:09.930 align:middle line:84%
When you said you couldn't
find her under her own name,

01:05:09.930 --> 01:05:12.790 align:middle line:84%
I put two and two together,
went the extra mile,

01:05:12.790 --> 01:05:16.240 align:middle line:90%
became a real private detective.

01:05:16.240 --> 01:05:20.020 align:middle line:84%
She had a right to see what
you had created in your film.

01:05:20.020 --> 01:05:22.710 align:middle line:84%
And I had the right
to finally meet her.

01:05:22.710 --> 01:05:24.050 align:middle line:90%
I'm glad I came.

01:05:24.050 --> 01:05:27.850 align:middle line:84%
And I'm really glad that
you're the one who invited me.

01:05:27.850 --> 01:05:30.920 align:middle line:84%
You know, guys, this is--
this is almost much more

01:05:30.920 --> 01:05:33.360 align:middle line:84%
than I could have hoped
for-- having both of you

01:05:33.360 --> 01:05:36.340 align:middle line:90%
here like this at the same time.

01:05:36.340 --> 01:05:37.150 align:middle line:90%
It's a lot to take.

01:05:37.150 --> 01:05:39.290 align:middle line:84%
It's not strange that
we're together at all.

01:05:39.290 --> 01:05:41.830 align:middle line:84%
It should have
happened years ago.

01:05:41.830 --> 01:05:43.510 align:middle line:84%
There's something I
wanted to say to you

01:05:43.510 --> 01:05:46.485 align:middle line:90%
since the day I met this man.

01:05:46.485 --> 01:05:48.640 align:middle line:90%
Thank you.

01:05:48.640 --> 01:05:51.190 align:middle line:84%
Is it OK if I ask you what
that thank you is about?

01:05:51.190 --> 01:05:52.590 align:middle line:90%
SUSAN: She knows.

01:05:52.590 --> 01:05:53.510 align:middle line:90%
I know.

01:05:53.510 --> 01:05:56.270 align:middle line:90%


01:05:56.270 --> 01:05:59.010 align:middle line:84%
And now I think it's
time we get to this party.

01:05:59.010 --> 01:06:00.860 align:middle line:84%
Everyone's wondering
where the director is.

01:06:00.860 --> 01:06:01.940 align:middle line:90%
Ah.

01:06:01.940 --> 01:06:03.610 align:middle line:84%
Well, you two have got
some confessing to do.

01:06:03.610 --> 01:06:04.090 align:middle line:90%
Uh-huh.

01:06:04.090 --> 01:06:06.056 align:middle line:84%
I want to find out how long
you guys have known each other

01:06:06.056 --> 01:06:08.530 align:middle line:84%
and gone through this
scheme [INAUDIBLE].

01:06:08.530 --> 01:06:12.190 align:middle line:90%
That's our little secret.

01:06:12.190 --> 01:06:14.174 align:middle line:90%
[INAUDIBLE].

01:06:14.174 --> 01:06:17.290 align:middle line:84%
I forgot how beautiful
Ashland this time is of year.

01:06:17.290 --> 01:06:18.970 align:middle line:90%
It's like magic.

01:06:18.970 --> 01:06:20.470 align:middle line:90%
It is magic.

01:06:20.470 --> 01:06:22.870 align:middle line:84%
And this is going to
be a great Christmas.

01:06:22.870 --> 01:06:24.720 align:middle line:90%
Shall we?

01:06:24.720 --> 01:08:00.704 align:middle line:90%